### ============================================================
### System Role Permissions — API Testing
### ============================================================
### System roles have built-in default permissions (no seeding needed).
### These endpoints let org admins customize permissions per role.
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3030/api
@token = PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

### ── Login as Org Admin ─────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@helenacoaching.com",
  "password": "ChangeMe123!"
}

### ============================================================
### READ: Get effective permissions for all system roles
### Returns defaults if no org-level overrides exist
### ============================================================

### Get all system role permissions (defaults + any overrides)
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles/system-roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get available permission groups (static definitions)
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================
### CUSTOMIZE: Override permissions for a specific role
### ============================================================

### Override Manager role — add IDP access
PUT {{baseUrl}}/roles/system-roles/manager
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "permissions": [
    "VIEW_CONFLICT_DASHBOARD",
    "ESCALATE_CONFLICT",
    "VIEW_CONFLICT_RESPONSES",
    "RUN_NEUROINCLUSION",
    "VIEW_NEUROINCLUSION_RESULTS",
    "VIEW_ALL_IDPS",
    "GENERATE_IDP",
    "UPDATE_IDP_MILESTONES",
    "VIEW_HUB"
  ]
}

### Override Coach role — add conflict dashboard access
PUT {{baseUrl}}/roles/system-roles/coach
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "permissions": [
    "VIEW_CONFLICT_DASHBOARD",
    "CONDUCT_INTERVIEWS",
    "VIEW_INTAKE_TEMPLATES",
    "VIEW_ALL_IDPS",
    "GENERATE_IDP",
    "UPDATE_IDP_MILESTONES",
    "VIEW_HUB"
  ]
}

### Override Employee (coachee) role — add journal and survey access
PUT {{baseUrl}}/roles/system-roles/coachee
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "permissions": [
    "TAKE_SURVEY",
    "VIEW_OWN_IDP",
    "UPDATE_IDP_MILESTONES",
    "VIEW_HUB"
  ]
}

### ============================================================
### RESET: Remove override and revert to platform defaults
### ============================================================

### Reset Manager to defaults
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/roles/system-roles/manager
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reset Coach to defaults
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/roles/system-roles/coach
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reset Employee to defaults
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/roles/system-roles/coachee
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================
### VERIFY: Check permissions again after changes
### ============================================================

### Verify — should show isOverridden flags
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles/system-roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
